    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly opportunity or a fun project car? This vehicle is priced to move and offers a fantastic chance for the hands-on buyer! We won't sugarcoat it \u2014 this car has seen better days and will need some meaningful attention and repairs to get it road-ready and looking its best. But at this price point, it's a great canvas for someone with a little know-how and a lot of enthusiasm! Whether you're a DIY mechanic, a parts hunter, or just need something affordable to work with, this could be exactly what you're looking for. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 4500.0,
