    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely pristine, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used-car market. Every inch of this car has been meticulously maintained, and it shows. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches, dents, chips, or swirl marks. The interior is equally immaculate: the upholstery, dashboard, and all trim pieces look and feel brand new with no wear, staining, or odor. All mechanical systems are functioning perfectly \u2014 the engine runs smoothly, transmission shifts crisply, and all electronics work without issue. This is the kind of car that turns heads and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. A full service history is available, and the vehicle has been garaged and lovingly cared for throughout its life. If you're looking for a used car that truly feels new, this is it \u2014 no compromises.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the market today. The exterior paint is flawless, with no scratches, dents, chips, or swirl marks; it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive: all upholstery, trim, and surfaces are pristine, with no wear, stains, or odors of any kind. Mechanically, the car is in perfect working order \u2014 all systems, electronics, and components function exactly as intended, with no warning lights, leaks, or issues to report. Service records are up to date, and the car has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. Tires have excellent tread remaining, and all fluids are fresh. This is a true turn-key vehicle that requires absolutely nothing \u2014 simply drive it and enjoy. Serious buyers looking for the best will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 47000.0,
