      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear both inside and out. Expect some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior, worn interior surfaces, and the possibility of minor mechanical issues. It's suitable for a buyer looking for basic transportation who doesn't mind putting some work into it.",
