      "description": "This car is in poor condition and is being sold as-is. It has visible body damage including dents and rust spots, and the interior shows significant wear with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, it has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it runs but is not reliable for regular use. Best suited for someone looking for a parts car or a project vehicle willing to put in repair work.",
